    "headline": "Community Tuesday- Our Open House",
    "body": "Our first Community Tuesday of the year will be held on October 23 from 5 to 7:30 PM . Please join us to see the great programs that we have to offer our students and the incredible work they accomplish daily. We look forward to seeing you here on the 23rd.",
