    "headline": "Fitness Training",
    "body": "At long last our NJROTC Cadets have a way to implement their physical fitness regime in safety and style. Today they used the new training stations at six areas around the jogging trail built earlier this year. The exercise equipment was funded through a $5,500 grant from the Spring Branch Education Foundation and in part through our Executive Director Sofia Petrou\\'s office. We appreciate this asset for the students of our Distinguished Unit.",
