    "year": 2007,
    "headline": "Strong Performance",
    "body": "NJROTC Cadets performed admirably during their Annual MilitaryInspection today at The Guthrie Center. Under the watchful eye of Area 10 Commander Mike Hale , many parents and Board of Trustees Theresa Kosmoski and Mary Grace Landrum , the cadets were assessed in Personnel Inspection, Basic Platoon marching Drill, Drill Team performances, Pass-In-Review. The cadet leadership then briefed Cdr. Hale on the unit and their personal goals, displayed their financial and inventory records, and wrapped it up with an exquisite luncheon prepared by our Culinary Arts students.",
