    "year": 2008,
    "headline": "Coming Soon To A Mailbox Near You",
    "body": "The Guthrie Center Course Selection Guide for 2008-2009 is coming soon to your home. This year the guide will look a little different but has all the information you need to make an informed decsion on the Guthrie classes you want to take next year. Watch your mail towards the end of the month for delivery.",
