    "body": "Movies, workshops, Q&A\\'s, interviewing directors and actors - this is all part of the Sundance experience our DF2 students are in the middle of right now. The students tell it best, so click on the link below to view their podcasts, photos and more http://guthriecenter.springbranchisd.com/DF/DF/Welcome.html",
