    "body": "Tonight at the CultureShapers awards ceremony, our school and district were proudly represented by Cristian Alvarez, Sean Giroir, Chris Leyendecker, Kate Phillips & Hannah Smith who all placed inthe top 10. These creative and innovative filmmakers each walked away with their award, a cash prize and the satisfaction of being among the top selected of hundreds of entries.",
