    "body": "Our NJROTC cadets were busy preparing for tomorrow\\'s meet in Tomball. Check out the video below for a first hand look! Right below that, you can view exerpts from the Drill Teams and Color Guard performance at the Tomball Meet on Saturday. FLASH - Feb 6 - Our Cadets Placed at Tomball and have been invited to compete at State for NJROTC Area 10 - an awesome accomplishment!",
