    "body": "This morning students loaded up their tools for competition (computers, monitors, hair styling items, etc) and boarded the bus for the SkillsUSA events andreturned with some great results. 3D Animation Zoe Sommers & Lizzy Herrera took 1st Place in Team Skills, and Lizzy also had her project earn a 1st Place award. In the Cosmetology competition, Cindy Lopez won 1st Place in Nail Care while Bora Im earned 1st in Nail Art. Congratulations to these students and all of our other winners who competed against their peers from around the Houston area. On Saturday, our NJROTC Orienteering Team of Hugo and Elier Rodriguez finished 2nd among the many teams competing at Jones State Park in Conroe.",
