    "date": "2008-03-27",
    "year": 2008,
    "headline": "End of A Visit",
    "body": "Six students and a teacher from the American Farm School in Thessaloniki, Greece spent the end of their 10 day USA visit with us today. We were honored to host Olga Fotiou, Helen Boutou, Fani Tasi, Kyros Sidiropoulos, Vaggelis Katsodonis, Stelios Balasis and teacher George Stambolides and show them the fine programs our students have to choose from in elective classes. Their school has an agricultural emphasis and is a prestigious school in the country of Greece. Someday we hope to send a delegation of our students to visit them and learn about the customs and way of life of teens in that part of the world.",
