    "headline": "And So It Goes",
    "body": "Our annual year-end crawfish boil allows us to take time for fellowship and farewells. This year we say goodbye to teachers Larry Haug and Laurie Ledbetter. We wish them all the best in their new endeavors, and hope you all have a safe and stressless summer.",
