    "date": "2008-06-06",
    "year": 2008,
    "headline": "Summer Sensations",
    "body": "This week students attending the annual Summer Career Carnival had a chance to tour the Omni Hotel , cook with the Culinary Arts students, visit our Ag Science Center and take a tour of Sam Houston State University \\'s many colleges. Next week they will visit Minute Maid Park , tour the Houston SPCA , visit the home office of Kirksey Architects , picnic at the Galleria and culminate with a trip to and tour of many exciting areas in Austin . The Career Carnival is organized by our counselor Beverly Litton and is a joint effort with Houston Community College . While it\\'s too late to get in this year\\'s action, check again next spring for the 2009 Summer Career Carnival.",
