    "headline": "Automotive Excellence",
    "body": "Auto Tech teacher Craig Clark was presented today with a plaque and letter of acknowledgement by the United States Air Force Education and Training Command in honor of being named Outstanding Technology Teacher for 2007-2008. Every year the USAF bestows this on a handful of educators around the USA. Congratulations Craig!",
