    "date": "2008-08-18",
    "year": 2008,
    "headline": "A Round of Applause",
    "body": "As our awesome staff returns for the start of 0809, we enjoyed a morning in the coliseum at the Convocation. In addition to wisdom imparted by our superintendent Duncan Klussmann , we were treated to inspiring speakers Clay Roberts talking about the 40 Assets and by Emmanuel Lopez , award-winning former CTE and Northbrook student.",
