    "year": 2008,
    "headline": "Back With Passion",
    "body": "It\\'s great to be back for another year! We are starting off with record enrollment of interested and excited students throughout our school and remote locations. Our students were met with smiles, new computers and equipment in many areas and a Culinary lab makeover. They also had the benefit of meeting our two newest teachers, Nikki Reed in Ag Science and Erin Land in Culinary Arts!",
