    "headline": "Busy Saturday",
    "body": "Today seemed like a regular school day with all of the activity around campus. NJROTC held a very successful fundraiser Car Wash, Architecture students held a \"Purge Party\", FFA students and families enjoyed their Kick Off Picnic with delicious boxed lunches made by Culinary Arts students, and the HVAC men were here trying to keep our facilities a bit more comfortable. I am always humbled by our students and staff who give up their free time to stay involved, spread the good word and have some fun!",
