    "id": "2008-09-09-3042",
    "date": "2008-09-09",
    "year": 2008,
    "headline": "Red Carpet Treatment",
    "body": "Superintendent Duncan Klussmann hosted over 50 Spring Branch Realtors today at The Guthrie Center. A superb gourmet meal of Grilled Beef Tenderloin, Prosciutto Wrapped Asparagus and Garlic Duchesse Potatoes was enjoyed by our area real estate experts as they were briefed by Duncan on the state of the district and the state of school financing in Texas. Thanks to our Culinary Arts students and teachers Jennifer Cardenas and Erin Land for pulling off an exemplary event with only 9 days of school under their belt!",
