    "date": "2008-09-11",
    "year": 2008,
    "headline": "We Remember",
    "body": "Today, as we prepare for the arrival of Hurricane Ike, we also take time to remember our fallen heros and the victims of September 11, 2001. Our students observed an extended moment of silence as our NJROTC Color Guard raised and lowered the flags to half-staff in honor of Patriot\\'s Day.",
