    "headline": "Spared",
    "body": "While Hurricane Ike came and went, he spared our school from any major damage. A little water here and there and a lot of debris, which was cleaned up today by our custodial staff and many of our NJROTC Cadets who donated their time and talent getting us ready to serve! Thanks everyone for your efforts.",
