    "body": "KHOU TV\\'s Deborah Duncan is joining with PDAP at Memorial High School on Tuesday, October 21st at 7PM to host their \"Teens and Risky Behavior\" seminar. PDAP (Palmer Drug Abuse Program) , a free,drug and alcohol recovery service has been serving the youth of Houston since 1971.",
