    "headline": "Weekend of Helping Hands",
    "body": "Architecture\\'s student organization OSA volunteered Saturday with Rebuilding Together Houston to brighten the life of an older Houstonian who\\'s home was in need of repair. NJROTC students had a lock-in Friday and then were in the Conroe area at the Memory Walk to End Alzheimer\\'s at Lone Star College. They helped man the stations for those raising money for this affliction that could affect many of us someday.",
