    "body": "NJROTC cadets had a successful innaugural meet on Saturday at West Brook HS in Beaumont. Overall the unit took 3rd place, with individual and team performances as follows: Armed Basic Drill 2nd Place, Armed Inspection 3rd Place, Unarmed Inspection 2nd Place, Color Guard 3rd Place, Male Athletics 1st Place, Female Athletics 2nd Place, Top Female Sit-ups earned by Monica Apolinar , and Top Male Sit- ups awarded to Cameron Sims .",
