    "body": "When a handful of chickens were found in Stratford High running the hallways, their staff tried to calm them down by tying their legs together. Fortunately, someone had the intuitiveness to contact our Ag Science program to find them a home and free them from bondage. The flapping, feathered fowls zip-ties were removed, and they now happily reside at the Ag Science Center on Brittmoore, eating bugs and bugging the animals.",
