    "body": "Here\\'s an easy way to help the National FFA . Campbell Soups will donate $1 (up to $250,000) for every click of the red barn on its website to the FFA scholarship and education programs. You can do this once a day, so please click and tell. Our Ag Science program thanks you! http://www.helpgrowyoursoup.com/supporting.aspx",
