    "headline": "What Is That",
    "body": "Tonight as our dilligent FFA Alumni Association parents met at the Ag Science Center to discuss details and upcoming events, the FFA student chapter met across the hall handling their business. The session I caught was unique - the members grouped into 5 teams with a common goal of creating a farm animal out of chewed gum. They had a lot of fun and the winning creations vaguely resembled a cat and a heifer.",
