    "body": "Our FFA Radio Team placed 2nd out of the 14 teams in Brenham today and will compete at the State level on December 5th and 6th at Sam Houston State University. Congratulations to Tyler First, Amy Higginbotham and Hannah Smith and FFA Advisor Nikki Reed for this accomplishment! We wish them the best as they vie against the top 20 teams from Texas in hopes of bringing a state title to SBISD.",
