    "body": "No, Chef Land is not putting out the latest culinary creation that baked a little long. As part of ourstaff development training, our Emergency Response Team demonstrated how to safely and correctly use fire extinguishers and reviewed our plans in case they are needed. One of our goals is to provide our students a safe and secure place to learn.",
