    "year": 2009,
    "headline": "FFA Show & Sale Is On The Way",
    "body": "The 31st Annual FFA Show and Sale is coming your way soon. Events this year include the Children\\'s Barnyard on Thursday, February 5 from 9 AM to 2 PM, the FFA Livestock Shows on Thursday and Friday evenings from 5 - 7 and culminating with the FFA Live Auction Saturday at 1PM. All events are open to the public, and of course, buyers are welcome and wanted. For more information, please contact our FFA Alumni Association at 713.335.9699. All FFA events are held at our farm at 1905 Brittmoore.",
