    "headline": "Not Conde Nast Quite Yet",
    "body": "Travel and Tourism students from the Omni Hotel Management program went to visit some of the tourist sites in Houston today courtesy of teacher Lorraine Hamilton . First stop was the Hilton of the America\\'s where former Hotel Management Intern, now HR director at the Hilton, met them and gave a tour. After leaving the Hilton they walked over to one of Houston\\'s newest tourist spots, Discover Green. They finished their tour at the House of Blues.",
