    "year": 2009,
    "headline": "Earthly Ideas",
    "body": "In celebration of Earth week, Architectural CAD students have constructed a maze in the courtyard. The maze, provided by Emerging Green Builders , raises awareness about the environment, LEED (Leadership in Energy and Environmental Design) and sustainability. The display will be on campus for viewing until May 8.",
