    "year": 2009,
    "headline": "Showing Support",
    "body": "NJROTC Cadets and Guthrie staff participated today at the 16th annual Running For The Arts that benefits the Education Foundation\\'s ARTS Partner Program, providing cultural opportunites for all SBISD students. Congratulations to the two dozen cadets and Elva Saldivar for donating their time towards this excellent cause.",
    "programs": [
      "NJROTC"
    ],
    "imageUrl": "https://guthrie-center.github.io/guthrie-media/uploads/2011/07/rfa.jpg",
    "source": "web"
