    "body": "June 14 - NJROTC\\'s Ashley Ruiz was the Top Female Athlete at Leadership Academy this past week. Cecilia Silva was the top female runner at 1.5 miles with a time of 9:51. Other cadets successfully completing the weeklong event include Elier Rodriguez, Justina Chapa, Ambar Balderas, Monica Apolinar, Cecilio Aguilar, Brian O’Connor and Elson Perez. These cadets continued their summer regime during the week of June 21 at Basic Leadership in Beaumont - Cecilia Silva, Justina Chapa (Graduate Assistants) , Cristina Enriquez, Me, Ruby Rivera, Jennifer Zapata, Eugenia Leal, Kevin Dang, Inez Capuchino (Graduate Assistant) , Tony Dinh, Joao DaSilva and Ruben Rincon.",
