    "body": "Last weekend we had students attend the Navy-Rice Football game and much more. This week our Architecture students will be at Rebuilding Together Houston giving their time and talent to help those in need. Our NJROTC will hold a lock in and Car Wash Saturday from 9 - 2 for Wreaths Across America. Cosmetology students will have services available to the public on Saturday as well. Next week our FFA students will begin activites with the Harris County Fair.",
