    "year": 2009,
    "headline": "Youth Leadership Forum",
    "body": "Seven Guthrie students attended the 8th Annual YLF today at the James A. Baker III Institute for Public Policy at Rice University. This prestigous event sponsored by Leadership Houston is designed to encourage and inspire high school juniors from across the Greater Houston area to acquire the knowledge and skills necessary to become agents of positive change in their communities. Col. Sluis chapperoned our star students Ambar Balderas, Cornessa Berry, Jonathan Cox, Ashley Ruiz, Cecilia Silva, Hannah Smythe and Savannah Williams.",
