    "year": 2009,
    "headline": "Chef's Surprise",
    "body": "Our Chef Training students created a marvelous holiday luncheon today for their family, friends and guests from The Art Institute of Houston , our long-standing higher education partner in this class. Many of our awesome Guthrie staff pitched in to help serve and clean after consuming the feast themselves. Everyone took in the beautiful snowfall ordered in specailly for this event by Art Institute Chef Michael Bargas. View photos of the event below.",
