    "headline": "Holiday Fun",
    "body": "FFA students and parents put on a great event this evening for community families at their annual Santa\\'s Farm. After spending hours and hours decorating and preparing for the night, their reward was watching and guiding the hundreds of guests enjoy this holiday treat.",
