    "date": "2010-01-08",
    "year": 2010,
    "headline": "Join Us At Our Community Tuesday",
    "body": "Our spring semester open house, Community Tuesday, will be this coming Tuesday, January 12th from 5 to 7:30 PM. You can stroll around the campus to visit our excitingprograms, meet our instructors and some students, and get involved in a sample lesson of what we do here daily. We are also pleased to have CPA Bob Stevenson , a Spring Branch resident, who will present his seminar \"Paying for College: Tax Strategies and Financial Aid.\" The event is free and open to the public.",
