    "year": 2010,
    "headline": "Learning the Ropes",
    "body": "Agricultural Science students Elvira Ayala, Andrew Johnson, Sofia Caylor, Allison Jubert and Claudia Martinez are in Austin today with teacher Christy Capps for Texas FFA Day at the State Capitol. They are learning about our state political process, specifically addressing agriculture and agricultural education, via workshops and presentations conducted by key political figures in Texas.",
