    "date": "2010-04-07",
    "year": 2010,
    "headline": "A Great Honor",
    "body": "Culinary Arts Instructor Jennifer Cardenas , Guthrie\\'s Teacher of the Year, has been named a finalist for SBISD\\'s Secondary Teacher of the Year . Congratulations Jennifer - you are so worthy and deserving of this honor and recognition! The three finalists interview on April 15th with the TOY committee who will choose the district\\'s Teacher of the Year. Good luck Jennifer!",
