    "date": "2010-05-26",
    "year": 2010,
    "headline": "OSA Helps Pay The Way",
    "body": "Sonia Greiner\\'s 3rd year Architectural Design students, Loraine Ng and Nilsen Sagastume, were the recipients of the annual Organization of Student Architects College Scholarship. Each student was awarded $1000 towards college expenses. Loraine will be attending UT Austin and Nilsen has been accepted to Pratt. Good luck to both of you.",
