    "headline": "Battle Of The Bands This Friday @ 6 for $5",
    "body": "The Guthrie Center will be holding their annual BATTLE OF THE BANDS this FRIDAY, May 6 with 7 bands from all over the district battling it out for $250 dollars cash! The battle begins at 6 o\\'clock sharp with \" Dairy Party \" from Stratford leading the battle. THIS FRIDAY! REMEMBER, the first band starts at 6 o\\'clock sharp so you need to arrive early to see them all! Tickets are $5 dollars at the door . Food and concessions will be sold. Be there! Proceeds benefit the Film & Photo Club . LINE UP 6:00 – 6:20 DAIRY PARTY 6:30 – 6:50 AUTUMNS ARISEN 7:00 – 7:20 RUNNER 7:30 – 7:50 SOBER IN THE MORNING 8:00 – 8:20 TWISTED MINDS 8:20 – 8:50 WRITE WHAT’S LEFT 9:00 – 9:20 OH NOSTALGIA",
