    "id": "2011-05-03-2238",
    "date": "2011-05-03",
    "year": 2011,
    "headline": "MGM High School Design Competition Results",
    "body": "Our Architectural Design department is proud to announce that 78 students entered the 21st annual Michael G. Meyers High School Design and Scholarship Competition . This competition is sponsored by the Houston Chapter of the American Institute of Architects. This year, the competition included students from 8 different area high schools. They were to design an Urban “Super” Market located in the Montrose area of Houston. The MGMC awards ceremony was held at the downtown office of the AIA on Friday, April 29, 2011. Ten students from Sonia Greiner and Xavier Martinez Architectural Design classes won recognition. Out of the 11 categories awarded, the Guthrie Center students received 8 of those awards. Student’s collectively received $7100 in scholarship prizes that includes admission to the 2011 University of Houston’s Architectural Summer Discovery Program. Luis Jimenez and Joe Landrum are repeat winners of this contest having won Best Visualization and 2nd Place Group respectively.. Honorable Mentions: Best Visualization: Luis Jimenez (NHS) Best Visualization: Gallery Martinez (WAIS) Best Detail Design: Zach Metzler (SWHS) Director’s Favorite: Eric Sorto (NHS) Individual Jorge Rebellon (SHS) Group Awards 3rd Place: Christine Nguyen (SHS) and Walter Mata (SWHS) 2nd Place: Joe Landrum (WAIS) and Issac Suarez (WAIS) Individual Awards 3rd Place: Mauricio Araiza (MHS) Thank you to the scholarship sponsors this year for their generous donations: Kirksey Architecture ArCH Foundation Avadek Bihner Chen Engineering Brookstone E&C Engineers Gensler Tandus Turner Construction Colorstone CW Lighting & Associates Lesco Putterman, Schark & Associates Lighting Thank you to this years Jurors: Cord Bowen March, MBA; Wendy Heger, AIA; Angel Rivera LEED AP, The Houston Architecture Foundation, The AIA-Houston Chapter, The MGMC Committee, Parents, and",
    "programs": [
      "Architectural Design"
    ],
    "imageUrl": "https://guthrie-center.github.io/guthrie-media/uploads/2011/05/Zach-Metzler.jpg",
    "source": "wordpress"
