    "date": "2011-10-10",
    "year": 2011,
    "headline": "NJROTC Team Excels At Annual Prairie View A&M Competition",
    "body": "The results from our NJROTC Prairie View A&M meet are in. Cadet Ruby Rivera earned a third place individual medal for female pushups completing 41 in a 120 second time-frame. Gabriel Tzoc earned a first place individual medal for male pushups with 104 for his two minute intense workout. The SB NJROTC Basic Orienteering Team of Cadets Marlene Alfaro, Corey Downs, Kristen Tabor and Christopher Martinez earned a first place trophy. Congratulations to all who participated against their peers from around the Gulf Coast Area.",
