    "id": "2011-12-01-4708",
    "date": "2011-12-01",
    "year": 2011,
    "headline": "104 Guthrie Students Invited To Join NTHS",
    "body": "For the past couple of years, we have explored having a chapter of the National Technical Honor Society at Guthrie for our students. This year teacher Linda Newnum took on the task with tenacity and success. The result is we have 104 Guthrie students who will be inducted into the inaugural NTHS chapter at The Guthrie Center. Today, seventy of them attended an orientation meeting at the school with co-sponsors Patty Nilsson and Sonia Greiner . NTHS offers opportunities for members to be part of a prestigious academic and career-focused organization, apply for dedicated national scholarships only for NTHS students, hold leadership positions, plan, organizes and conduct community service events and earn recognition at graduation. We look forward to a busy and productive spring with these find young men and women. In alpha order by last name, here are our NTHS inductees, class of 2011-2012. Michael Aldridge Samantha Andrade Ashton Belcher Spencer Bennett Vance Berk Claudet Berrones Paige Brown Michael Cabrera Jessica Calzada Juana Campos Natalie Cantor Mirna Cardenas Cindy Chan Erin Clark Ricardo Coria Rene DelaCalleja Antonio Delacruz Ai-Van Do Lindsay Doler Samuel Dunlap Jeremy Dyer Kattia Espinoza Vanessa Espinoza Cristian Garcia Christian Garcia Lucero Gonzalez Armando Guerra Llualmer Guevara Addison Haight Ciara Harrison Jessica Hayes Dulce Hernandez Jacqueline Hernandez Gloria Hernandez Melissa Iracheta Zain Irshad Andrew Johnson Jordan Jump Andrew Kelly Samuel Kim Javier Lagunas Yi Chieh Lee Christian Lee Sang Heon Lee Daniel Leeper Khanhtran Levu Destiny Lewis Samuel Lopez Cecilia Lopez Erick Lopez Saul Lopez Alexis MacPherson Ana Martinez Ericka Mayorga Michael McInroe Isabel Melgoza Elizabeth Mojica Samantha Moon Chan Moon Evan Moore Anjanee Munidasa Mohammad Naraghi Keira Noble Shannon Olson Emanuel Paredes Kennya Paredes Duane Patterson Jenny Payton David Pham",
