    "headline": "Competition Team Dinner And Fundraiser",
    "body": "The first Guthrie Culinary Arts competition teams to compete in the ProStart Invitational held a fundraiser dinner and demonstration on February 7 @ 5:30 PM. The ProStart competition consist of two events. The Management Team\\' s job is to develop a proposal for the next big thing in restaurants conceptually and present it to a panel of industry judges. The Culinary Team \\'s challenge is to prepare a three-course meal in one hour using only two gas burners with no available running water or electricity. At stake in the nationals are up to $34 million in scholarships. Good luck to our teams and come out and support their efforts.",
