    "headline": "Animation Majors",
    "body": "Animation 2 student Joey (Qiaoyu) Yang from Stratford has been accepted by the University of Texas - Dallas (UTD) and will be pursuing a degree in Arts and Technology. Joey, a first generation immigrant from Kunming, China spends his non-school time hanging out with friends, going to the movies, creating animations and sketching. Westchester Academy senior and 4th year animation student Marvin Mendoza has been accepted into the Motion Graphics Program at The Ringling College of Art and Design in Sarasota Florida. Marvin is a self-motivated when it comes to art projects and spends spare time at the movies and playing video games, and actively while playing tennis, biking, rock climbing and swimming. Marvin\\'s brother Edwin is also in Animation in his second year.",
