    "body": "On Saturday March 29, 2014 our Eagles competed at the Magnolia NJROTC Deep Sea Meet and took first place in the 1.5 mile run and academics and placed second in orienteering. Brittany Gonzales , a junior from Spring Woods, took second place in female cross-country and Bryan Wambui took second place in male cross-country. Check out the video highlights of the events courtesy of CDR Coufal.",
