    "date": "2014-04-01",
    "year": 2014,
    "headline": "Blood Drive Successful",
    "body": "Yesterday the Spring Branch FFA Chapter organized and facilitated a blood drive in memory and support of a young girl from Texas. The blood drive, taking place at our own Guthrie Center, collected over 70 donations of blood through the time and effort of over 100 volunteers as well as donors. This means that up to 216 lives can be saved from the success of this one event. Way to go Spring Branch FFA!",
